&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; rajinikanth ( english : dear rajinikanth ) is a 1984 tamil film directed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the film stars rajinikanth , meena , and ambika with jaishankar , raadhika and bhagyaraj in guest roles . it has positive reviews and praised the portrayal of child artist meena 's performance and mainly rajinikanth 's excellent acting .